- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper may use natural language processing techniques to analyze the Twitter data. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is also a possible category as the paper studies the relationship between weather and human mood, which is a topic in social and behavioral sciences.
